---
title: Creamy Tomato & Chorizo Fettuccine with Rocket & Parmesan Salad
description: Golden strands of fettuccine combine with tomato, cream and smokey chorizo to create an elegant meal fit for only the best. Add
a sharp rocket and Parmesan salad for crunch and dinner is complete.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/nz-creamy-tomato-chorizo-fettuccine-f25fca63.jpg
